n\ge 2,
\frac{2^n+3}{2^n+4^n}=\frac{2^n+3}{2^n(1+2^n)}\le\frac{2\cdot 2^n}{2^n(1+2^n)}\le\frac{2\cdot 2^n}{2^n\cdot 2^n}=\frac{2}{2^n}.
